                   ARP-SH1 GENERAL LIBRARY MANUAL

NAME
    screen -- Screen management

SYNOPSIS
    screen = require "screen"
    screen.push!
    screen.readonly!

DESCRIPTION
    Create, alter, and manage terminal screens.

    FUNCTIONS

        push!
            Create a new screen that is pushed on top of the
            previous screen.
        pop!
            Delete the screen on top.
        count!
            Return the number of active screens.
        readonly!
            Set the screen to readonly so the user cannot add any
            characters.